common_filenames.description: ATT_US.ipcc - Carrier bundle filename if your carrier is AT&T and your country is the United States.
TMOBILE_AU.ipcc - Carrier bundle filename if your carrier is T-Mobile and your country is Australia.
VERIZON_US.ipcc - Carrier bundle filename if your carrier is Verizon and your country is the United States.
SPRINT_US.ipcc - Carrier bundle filename if your carrier is Sprint and your country is the United States.
